Package com.yardi.userServices

Class SessionInfo

java.lang.Object
com.yardi.userServices.SessionInfo
public class SessionInfo extends Object
Container to hold information about the session. When html pages need information about the session they will do a post to SessionInfoSerice which will update this container and return it as JSON back to the html page.
